title: Exhaust Sound: MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust on a Audi S3
description: This eye-catching Audi sounds equally impressive with a Magnaflow Cat-Back Exhaust.

asset.title: MagnaFlow Audi S3 Cat-Back Exhaust System - Sound Clip
asset.description: Made in the USA and engineered to last, MagnaFlow performance exhausts system deliver the sound you want and the power you need. MagnaFlow is the right exhaust for your daily driver, track star or custom show stopper Audi. With power support options, black or polished finished and even systems to satisfy your ears desire for more or less sound, you can choose the MagnaFlow system that no only fits your car but satisfies your personal tastes and needs.
